### ========================================
### 27 - File Uploads
### Profile Images, Referral & Chart Attachments
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### PROFILE IMAGE
### ----------------------------------------

### Upload profile image
POST {{baseUrl}}/files/profile-image/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ProfileBoundary

------ProfileBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/avatar.jpg
------ProfileBoundary--

### Delete profile image
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/files/profile-image/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------
### REFERRAL ATTACHMENTS
### ----------------------------------------

### Upload referral attachment
POST {{baseUrl}}/files/referral-attachments/{{referralId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----ReferralBoundary

------ReferralBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="referral-doc.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/referral-doc.pdf
------ReferralBoundary--

### Get referral attachments
GET {{baseUrl}}/files/referral-attachments/{{referralId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete referral attachment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/files/referral-attachments/{{referralId}}/{{attachmentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

